WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.000
Can you see this thing?

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:03.920
It has support for your back

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:07.160
in the correct curvature that your back should be in.

00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:09.620
And I don't know how else to show you, but look,

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.020
you sit in it.

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:16.380
You sit, and then you lean back,

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.580
and it takes all the tension.

00:00:21.240 --> 00:00:22.880
All the tension off of your back.

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:24.240
I could seriously fall asleep here,

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:25.080
but I'm not gonna.

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:25.640
If you want one,

00:00:25.640 --> 00:00:26.940
it's linked right here.

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:29.440
If you know back pain like I know back pain,

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:32.120
you know that there's almost nothing you won't pay

00:00:32.120 --> 00:00:33.320
to make the pain go away.

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:37.780
And I am in love with this thing.
